        <h1>Activity Viz</h1>
        <p class="centerText">
          Kinect Data Activity Visualization is designed to be an add-on visualization tool to the existing Kinect data analysis programs such as <a href="https://tla.mpi.nl/tools/tla-tools/elan/" target="_blank" class="no-ajaxy">ELAN</a> and <a href="http://chronoviz.com/" target="_blank" class="no-ajaxy">ChronoViz</a> for Gesture Researchers.
        </p>
